      <div class="faq-group">
        <h2 class="faq-group-title">The Product</h2>
        <div class="accordions">
          <div class="accordion open">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>What is Happie Fungi Fusion?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Happie Fungi Fusion is a functional mushroom sparkling drink with 2,000mg of dual-extracted Lion's Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi per can. It's designed to support focus, energy, and calm — without alcohol, caffeine, or artificial ingredients.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Is this a psychedelic mushroom product?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Absolutely not. Happie contains functional/adaptogenic mushrooms — Lion's Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi. These are entirely different from psilocybin mushrooms. They are legal in all 50 states, non-psychoactive, and supported by decades of clinical research for their health benefits.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>How much caffeine does it have?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Zero caffeine. The energy and focus you feel comes from Cordyceps supporting ATP production and Lion's Mane supporting neural function — not from stimulating your adrenal system. No caffeine means no crash, no dependency, and no disrupted sleep.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Is it alcoholic?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">No. Happie Fungi Fusion contains zero alcohol. It's a completely non-alcoholic sparkling beverage suitable for all ages and any occasion. You can drink it in the morning, at work, while driving, or anywhere you'd drink a sparkling water.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>What does it taste like?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Like a premium sparkling juice — not like a supplement. Blue Razzberry is tart and candy-bright. Mango Mimosa is tropical and lightly sweet. Watermelon is clean, juicy, and refreshing. None of them taste "earthy" or medicinal. That was non-negotiable for us.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>How many calories per can?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">40 calories per can, sweetened with a small amount of organic light blue agave nectar. No refined sugar, no artificial sweeteners, no sugar alcohols that cause digestive issues.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-group">
        <h2 class="faq-group-title">Health & Safety</h2>
        <div class="accordions">
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Is it safe to drink daily?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes. Happie is formulated for daily use — that's actually when the functional mushroom benefits are most pronounced. The adaptogenic effects of Lion's Mane and Reishi build over time with consistent use. Most subscribers report noticeable differences after 2–4 weeks of daily consumption.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Can I drink it if I'm pregnant or nursing?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">We recommend consulting your healthcare provider before consuming any supplement product during pregnancy or while nursing. While functional mushrooms are natural and widely consumed, individual circumstances vary and a medical professional is best positioned to advise you.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Will it interact with my medications?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Functional mushrooms are generally well-tolerated, but if you're on blood thinners, immunosuppressants, or diabetes medication, please consult your doctor. Reishi in particular has mild blood-thinning and immune-modulating effects that could interact with certain prescriptions.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Is it vegan and gluten-free?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes to both. Happie Fungi Fusion is 100% vegan, gluten-free, non-GMO, and contains no animal products. All mushroom extracts are cultivated (not wild-harvested or derived from animals).</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Is every batch third-party tested?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes — every single batch. We test for heavy metals, microbial contamination, pesticides, potency (beta-glucan content), and purity. Every can has a QR code linking to the full Certificate of Analysis (COA) for that batch. You should always be able to verify what you're consuming.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-group">
        <h2 class="faq-group-title">Orders & Shipping</h2>
        <div class="accordions">
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>How fast does it ship?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Orders ship within 1 business day from our Northern California warehouse. Standard shipping is 3–5 business days. Expedited options are available at checkout.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Do you offer free shipping?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes — free shipping on all orders over $75. A 6-pack is $23.99, so two 6-packs qualifies. Our 12-pack options also qualify automatically.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Where do you ship?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">We currently ship to 40+ US states. Due to varying state regulations around functional supplements, some states may have restrictions. Your address at checkout will confirm availability.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>What's your return policy?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you're not happy — for any reason — contact us and we'll make it right. We want you to love Happie, and we stand behind that completely.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-group">
        <h2 class="faq-group-title">Subscriptions</h2>
        <div class="accordions">
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>How does Subscribe & Save work?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Choose Subscribe & Save at checkout to get 20% off every order, delivered automatically on your chosen schedule (monthly or every 2 months). You'll never run out, and you save every time. Cancel, pause, or skip anytime from your account — no fees, no hassle.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Can I cancel my subscription?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Yes — anytime. Log into your account, go to subscriptions, and cancel with one click. No cancellation fees, no hidden terms. We'd rather earn your business every month than trap you in it.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion">
            <button class="accordion-trigger" type="button"><span>Can I change my subscription frequency?</span><span class="acc-icon">+</span></button>
            <div class="accordion-body">Absolutely. You can switch between monthly and bi-monthly, skip a delivery, or change your flavor from your account dashboard at any time.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

